### 1. Create a Matchmaking Queue
POST {{matchmakingUrl}}/queues/{{queueId}}
    ?name=ManualTestQueue
    &requiredPlayers=10
    &region=EUW
    &mode=RANK_BASED

### 2. Create Player Profiles
POST {{matchmakingUrl}}/players?id={{p1}}&username=zezin
