### 6. Check Lobby Status (Poll until matched)
# @name getLobby
GET {{matchmakingUrl}}/tickets/c8c2c2c2-dfc8-4e25-81c8-23706f64753d/lobby

### 7. Accept the Match (All 10 players)
@matchId = 02207661-701a-40ba-b2ee-fb1e58b825d2

POST {{matchmakingUrl}}/tickets/matches/{{matchId}}/accept?playerId={{p1}}
###
POST {{matchmakingUrl}}/tickets/matches/{{matchId}}/accept?playerId={{p2}}
