### 8. Link Match to Riot ID (External ID)
@riotMatchId = EUW1_7836018871
PUT {{matchmakingUrl}}/tickets/matches/{{matchId}}/link
    ?externalGameId={{riotMatchId}}

### 9. Complete Match
POST {{matchmakingUrl}}/tickets/matches/{{matchId}}/complete

### 10. Verify Results
GET {{rankingUrl}}/players/{{p1}}/queue?queueId={{queueId}}
###
GET {{historyUrl}}/matches/{{riotMatchId}}
